VHMIS DOCKER
============

# Inside

* CentOS 7.
* Default httpd, mariadb (ship with Centos7).
* php7 from webstatic repo.
* Lastest icu library from ICU project.
* Custom php7-intl module.

# Install

    docker build -t vhmis .

# Run as services

    docker run -d -P --name vhmis_server \
               -v VHMIS_FRAMEWORK:/vhmis/Framework \
               -v VHMIS_SYSTEM:/vhmis/VhmisSystem \
               -v VHMIS_ROOT:/vhmis/WebRoot \
               -v VHMIS_LIBS:/vhmis/Libs \
               -v DATA:/data \
               vhmis
